---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
	<header class="text-white">
	<img class="w-full mx-auto" src="/header_bg.png" alt="Horizons Equinox Background" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-linear-to-t from-black via-black/70 to-transparent"></div>
		
	<div class="absolute top-1/8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full text-center">
        <img class="w-1/2 mx-auto mb-4" src="/equinox_logo.png" alt="Horizons Equinox Logo" />
        <div class="text-white">
            <h1 class="font-futura text-[3rem] font-bold mb-4">August 14-16 @ The GrEEK Campus, Cairo, Egypt</h1>
            <h2 class="font-futura text-3xl mt-2 font-normal">Code for 35 hours, <br> Get invited to a 3-day hackathon adventure</h2>
        </div>
    </div>
	<main class="bg-black text-white px-4 py-20 text-center">
		<section class="mb-8">
			<div class="absolute bottom-20 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 translate-y-1/3">
            <div class="p-1 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r from-[#4C54E6] via-[#E02E6A] to-[#EC7A0F]">
                <button class="font-futura text-2xl font-bold bg-white text-black px-14 py-2 rounded-full block">
                    get started!
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
		</section>

		<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
			<p class="font-futura text-5xl leading-tight mb-16">
				This August, we are bringing together 80+ teen coders from all around the world to join us for a free 3-day hackathon adventure in Egypt, <b>Horizons Equinox</b>.
			</p>
			<h1 class="font-karim text-[9.5rem] py-0 mb-0">
				All for free!
			</h1>
			<p class="font-futura text-2xl leading-tight mb-16">
				Free meals & snacks * Local transport * Event swag <br>
				Flight stipends available for extra hours
			</p>
		</section>

</section>
<section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
	<p class="font-futura text-4xl leading-tight">Create something new, get to see the pyramids of Giza up-close, code with new friends, ride a cruise down the Nile, and get immersed in Egyptian culture all in the span of 3 days!
	</p>
<section>
	<!-- image of how to qualify -->
</section >
<section class="mt-10">
	<img src="/cats.png" alt="Cats" class="w-3/4 mx-auto" />


	<!-- past hack club ebents -->
</section>

<section class="bg-black text-white py-20 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-center font-karim text-[8.5rem] mb-8">FAQs</h1>
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-12">
            <div>
                <h2 class="font-karim text-5xl font-bold mb-3">What is Hack Club</h2>
                <p class="font-futura text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
                    Hack Club is a global 501(c)(3) nonprofit based in the United States built by teens to support teen coders and we’ve run 500+ hackathons and events worldwide online and in-person.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class="font-karim text-5xl font-bold mb-3">Who can attend?</h2>
                <p class="font-futura text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
                    Teenagers aged 13–18 from any part of the world!
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class="font-karim text-5xl font-bold mb-3">How do stipends work?</h2>
                <p class="font-futura text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
                    For each additional hour you code you get $8.5 US Dollars credits which can be used to purchase flight stipends. So if you code 20 more hours thats 20 hours x $8.5/hour = $170
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-12 md:pl-16 md:border-l md:border-white">
            <div>
                <h2 class="font-karim text-5xl font-bold mb-3">How do I qualify?</h2>
                <p class="font-futura text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
                    There are 3 simple steps:<br>
                    1. Sign up via Horizons<br>
                    2. Code for 35+ hours<br>
                    3. You're qualified!
                </p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h2 class="font-karim text-5xl font-bold mb-3">Where can I find travel information?</h2>
                <p class="font-futura text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
                    We'll have a travel guide with visa, flight and arrival/departure details added here before June :)
                </p>
            </div>

			<div>
                <h2 class="font-karim text-5xl font-bold mb-3">I have more questions</h2>
                <p class="font-futura text-2xl font-normal leading-tight">
                    You can reach out to us via equinox@horizons.hackclub.com or have a Zoom call with one of the organisers :)
                </p>
            </div>
            <div>
</section>


	</main>

</Layout>
